Business Brief -- American Stores Co.:
   Definitive Pact Reached
   On Sales to Albertson's
The sale, subject to certain conditions, is expected to be
completed in April. The stores, which operate under the
Jewel/Osco name, are in Texas, Oklahoma, Arkansas and
Florida. American Stores said the sale is part of its
strategy to shed underperforming stores and concentrate on
its more profitable markets.
   American Stores and Albertson's are both grocery
retailers.